            <td colspan="2" class="titulo2" valign="top">Who Is That Boy? <span
 class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue12/william-bedford/bio.php"
 class="link3">William Bedford</a></span></td>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
            <td><img src="/images/spacer.gif" alt="" border="0"
